N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 253.21 - Decision and order

State Regulations

Upon completion of a proceeding, the hearing officer
shall issue a decision and order, ruling or report and recommendations as
appropriate to the proceeding. Notes
